Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.79,0:00:03.31,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do not come inside of me ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.31,0:00:05.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Stop messing with Akira!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.80,0:00:07.82,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.82,0:00:10.82,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I won't do anymore what you dislike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.82,0:00:14.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But please, just remember this one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.84,0:00:18.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm on your side,\NAkira and yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.41,0:00:21.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, will you be by my side?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.32,0:00:23.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.80,0:00:27.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll be by your side always.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.32,0:00:29.29,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.29,0:00:33.31,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm absolutely not buying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:38.31,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You too, one day,\Nwill abandon Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.30,0:00:45.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please, wait. \N{\3c&H3C2A21&}Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.32,0:00:47.29,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Until you appear,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.29,0:00:49.79,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira and I were doing just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.48,0:00:56.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's concerning a romance between psychiatrist and patient, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.56,0:00:57.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N{\3c&H3C2A21&}Patients have
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.92,0:01:02.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,feelings and attitudes\Ntowards important people for them,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:06.31,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and when those feelings\Nare transferred to the therapist, that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.31,0:01:08.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,it's called transference.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.30,0:01:11.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,When the feelings are transferred, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:14.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So transference is,\Nthe projection of feelings onto the therapist,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:16.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,who has come to represent
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.30,0:01:19.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,some important person from the patient's past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:25.31,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That transference may be\Na positive transition or
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.31,0:01:28.82,Default 1,,0,0,0,,a negative transition.\N{\3c&H3C2A21&}Positive transition ..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.82,0:01:32.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In circumstances where the patient\Nfeels like in love with the therapist,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.30,0:01:35.31,Default 1,,0,0,0,,generally on that case,\Nthe patient works cooperatively,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.31,0:01:37.82,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and the treatment is often effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:41.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, this time it's the opposite,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:46.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,it's the therapist the one\Nwho responds to those transference feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.32,0:01:49.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In the patient's mind,\Nwho is falling in love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.30,0:01:52.31,Default 1,,0,0,0,,that important person\Nwould be replaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.31,0:01:54.79,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Huh? And the patient would be considered
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.79,0:01:57.31,Default 1,,0,0,0,,as something as a lover,\Nis it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.31,0:01:58.81,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In Psychology,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:00.83,Default 1,,0,0,0,,that is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.83,0:02:02.87,Default 1,,0,0,0,,called counter-transference.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.87,0:02:05.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,counter-transference..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:06.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Love..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.80,0:02:09.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Love is\Nonly a transitory mental disorder,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.32,0:02:11.29,Default 1,,0,0,0,,although you told us that,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.29,0:02:14.29,Default 1,,0,0,0,,even if I keep telling myself that,\Nand keep stepping on the brake,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.29,0:02:17.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm on my limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.30,0:02:21.35,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If this continues, the break\Nwill break and I'll be running wildly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:23.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Let's settle down a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.39,0:02:25.82,Default 1,,0,0,0,,May I?\NRunning wildly can lead to accidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.82,0:02:29.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Just look,\Nlet's take some distance between vehicle-to-vehicle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.32,0:02:32.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He gets\Ntoo obsessed when it comes to patients
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:36.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,until he can't see anything else,\Neven though it's not the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:39.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Who are you talking about? Rintaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:44.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, to go beyond the boundaries of doctors and patients\Nit's absolutely not allowed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.36,0:02:45.33,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, that is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.33,0:02:48.33,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Moreover, the other party is a geisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.33,0:02:50.81,Default 1,,0,0,0,,A geisha? You mean Yumeno?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.88,0:02:54.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Araki,\Nwhy do you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:56.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No, just that when at Shinbashi,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.20,0:02:58.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I happened to overhear that there was a popular geisha
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:02:59.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,there called like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:02.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, Rintaro..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:08.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Regarding a psychiatrist, falling in love\Nis more hassle than what it's worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:09.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,that's what you told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:11.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,When in love, the male hormone in men will increase,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:13.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and will no longer hear\Nthe story of patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:17.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Fukuhara-kun, Is countertransference\Nhappening to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:19.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is that possible? \N{\3c&H3C2A21&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:22.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you in love with the other party,\Nprecisely with a patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:25.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No,\Nthere's no female patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:26.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,A male patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:28.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr., are you listening to my story? \N{\3c&H4B372D&}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:32.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sure, doctor's male hormones\Nhave increased too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:35.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No, that should not be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.04,0:03:36.83,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Fukuhara-san, what should we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.83,0:03:39.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? Fukuhara kun!\N{\3c&H533D32&}It's okay, my male hormones..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.04,0:03:42.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry, to interrupt your role-playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:43.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No, no. What's happening? Kawakami-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:46.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's about my friend Otaki Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:49.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Otaki Nami-san is under Fukuhara-kun's care, right?\N{\3c&H533D32&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:51.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. please, do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:53.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It looks like Nami's disease has relapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:55.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, she came.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:56.85,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:59.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yoko!\NJust in time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.48,0:04:02.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you know, please, lend me 200,000!\NI'll return you soon, with interests.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.48,0:04:04.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Nami please, I'm asking you\Nopen your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:07.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You know how much your mother is worried about you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.44,0:04:10.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If I get the ten thousand betting ticket,\NI'll repay immediately all my debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:14.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It went up again.\N{\3c&H533D32&}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.76,0:04:17.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Buy more, buy more.\NInvest all the 7 million
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:20.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be bad if you don't return those 7 million..\N{\3c&H533D32&}Put these too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:22.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Told you, the cash won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.52,0:04:24.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hurry, move out, enough..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:26.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,How do I do it? How?\N{\3c&H533D32&}All?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.36,0:04:28.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,All, all!\NCome on, do it, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:32.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Enter, got it, enter\NBuy it, buy it! I'm going for real now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:33.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's a sure bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:36.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It went up!\NDidn't it go up! See!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:38.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's going up, isn't it?\NIs moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:42.79,Self tought,,0,0,0,,So, now let's move forward with no fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.79,0:04:46.81,Self tought,,0,0,0,,I'm on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.81,0:04:50.30,Self tought,,0,0,0,,This is a story of a doctor that saves
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:52.82,Self tought,,0,0,0,,the lost sheep of this modern era.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:05:02.30,Self tought,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:06.80,Self tought,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the late introduction,\NI'm a psychiatrist, Hino Rintaro
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:17.80,Self tought,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:37.31,Self tought,,0,0,0,,She is\Na typical case of gambling addiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:39.32,Self tought,,0,0,0,,She has spent 3 months hospitalized,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.32,0:05:42.32,Self tought,,0,0,0,,with Fukuhara-kun being in charge\Nof her treatment, but
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:44.82,Self tought,,0,0,0,,it seems like she has relapsed into her old habits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:49.29,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Otaki-san .
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:53.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Fukuhara
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:56.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you have a little talk with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:02.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:06.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for breaking my promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:11.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Otaki-san, please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:14.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please, it's enough... Leave me alone.\N{\3c&H3C2A21&}No, I won't leave you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:17.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter what I do with my life,\Nit's my own choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:21.79,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Kawakami-san is seriously worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:25.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And I am your doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:27.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I won't leave you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.41,0:06:31.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Otaki-san, please recall\Nthose 3 painful months
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:33.29,Default 1,,0,0,0,,in rehabilitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.29,0:06:35.31,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Didn't we persevere together?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:38.31,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You just can't throw out
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:41.31,Default 1,,0,0,0,,all of that in this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:48.33,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:55.31,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:57.81,Self tought,,0,0,0,,"Positive transference ..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:02.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since you contacted with your house
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.30,0:07:04.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Today you'll be staying here, please
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:06.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,that was Fukuhara told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:12.81,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry,\Nwe'll put this under custody for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.81,0:07:14.81,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Wait..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:21.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:24.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Otaki Nami-san has devoted to gambling
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.32,0:07:26.31,Default 1,,0,0,0,,since two years ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:30.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes, she was engaged with a colleague\Nfrom the company in which she worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:33.33,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And even though the wedding date has been decided,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.33,0:07:36.33,Default 1,,0,0,0,,she broke off the engagement when she discovered he was cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:40.82,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It became hard to stay in the company,\Nand when she change her job,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:43.31,Default 1,,0,0,0,,her mood became unstable..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:46.31,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And from that time, she began to get into gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:50.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Her savings for her marriage, she spent them all
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:54.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and at the end,\Nthe debts started to pile up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:58.79,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:08:00.81,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:03.29,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:06.79,Default 1,,0,0,0,,For the repayment she even involved\Nher mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:14.82,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Unable to be indifferent to such Nami-san,\Nat the request of Kawakami-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:18.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Fukuhara-kun started the treatment six months ago.\N{\3c&H533D32&}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:23.85,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1\u1}"I'm okay..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:28.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1\u1}even without gambling"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:31.79,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1\u1}"I'm okay even without..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:34.31,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino, please do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.31,0:08:37.79,Default 1,,0,0,0,,As expected, Fukuhara-san\Ncan't do anything to help her..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.88,0:08:41.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I think Fukuhara-kun is doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:43.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, why \Nafter 3 months of the medical treatment
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:45.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,does she relapse?\N{\3c&H533D32&}Kawakami-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.20,0:08:49.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Gambling addiction is not a disease that will heal so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:52.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Although it seems painful your friend's suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:55.81,Default 1,,0,0,0,,we should proceed carefully at this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.81,0:08:58.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:00.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:09.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.93,0:09:12.81,Default 1,,0,0,0,,One more time, I need you to get 10 million somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:15.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please!\N{\3c&H533D32&}The other day, didn't I pass it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:17.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Can I help you?\N{\3c&H533D32&}Those..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.32,0:09:21.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,those have disappeared
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.80,0:09:23.82,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's already impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.82,0:09:27.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Don't say that ...\NI'm really in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.84,0:09:30.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This will be the last time..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:33.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Help your mother..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:39.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even if I beg, won't you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:43.79,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Enough! It would have been better not to have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.85,0:09:57.81,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.\N{\3c&H533D32&}What? I didn't listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.81,0:09:59.83,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'll do something
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:01.79,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:05.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,After all, you are mom's child.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.32,0:10:08.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:11.82,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:14.87,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira..Akira..Akira
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:19.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,200,000?\NDoes Nami have debts again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:25.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Aunt, as I'm also attending her,\NI'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:29.82,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's that so..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:34.33,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Don't give up!, Fukuhara-san\N{\3c&H533D32&}Ah.. yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:38.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Let's go gambling with Nami-san, tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:41.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What?\N{\3c&H533D32&}Please, invite Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.52,0:10:43.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:46.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Fukuhara-kun,\Nthis treatment will be gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:49.83,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So now, you\Nabsolutely can't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.16,0:10:53.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:57.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please tell her come at exactly 6:00 to the examination room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.04,0:11:00.83,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Otaki-san, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:13.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Otaki-san, Dr. Hino wants
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.32,0:11:16.82,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you to come to the examination room at 6 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:21.31,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino wants?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:25.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What he wants is to gamble with Otaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:34.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What is Dr. Hino thinking to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.24,0:11:37.31,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the inexperienced me, has no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:39.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:43.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm your attending doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:48.83,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I want to do what it's at my hand and\Ncontinue to treat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:04.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You wrote this note while struggling against
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.48,0:12:07.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,your desire in order to get back on your own feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:18.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,At 6 o'clock..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:22.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'd like you not to go to the examination room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.24,0:12:36.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,"Chō" is even, "Han" is odd
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:40.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Fukuhara-kun you'll be losing against Nami-san if you don't practice .
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:41.82,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.60,0:12:46.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. I'll be leaving first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.56,0:12:48.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're picking him up?\N{\3c&H533D32&}I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:51.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please tell the boy to come and play
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:54.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,once in a while.\N{\3c&H533D32&}Yes, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.16,0:12:57.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even without gambling, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:13:23.31,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even without gambling, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.31,0:13:24.81,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even without gambling..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:29.82,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.82,0:13:31.35,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:33.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr., one dice didn't get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.39,0:13:35.31,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:39.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Fukuhara-kun, could you pick it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:41.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:45.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Okay, Dr., once more, from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:48.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:50.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Enough, doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:52.86,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry.\N{\3c&H3C2A21&}Okay, one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:53.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:14:05.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even without gambling, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:07.81,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.81,0:14:09.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Now, get hyped, get hyped
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:11.34,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Chō!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:15.31,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Fukuhara-san.\Nget hyped, get hyped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.31,0:14:17.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, Chō. \N{\3c&H533D32&}Isn't it Han?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.80,0:14:21.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,ah.. Han.\N{\3c&H533D32&}Chō-han, the pieces are equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.30,0:14:23.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm okay, even without gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:32.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm okay, even without gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.38,0:14:37.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm okay, even without gambling.\NI'm okay, even without gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.80,0:14:39.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm okay..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.79,0:14:50.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:52.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Game!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:54.82,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Double ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:05.83,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Otaki-san, don't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:10.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please move away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:13.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The results if you continue gambling,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:15.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Otaki-san should be the one who knows that the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.03,0:15:17.81,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's not just money what you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:24.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,How about your mother taken over
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.56,0:15:26.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,your debts to help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:32.81,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.86,0:15:36.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:39.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:01.79,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately\Nthe gambling parlor is now closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:03.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:06.33,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The time now is 6:00 past 1 minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.20,0:16:11.83,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, that is because Nami-san and Dr. Fukuhara joined forces
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:14.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you were able to endure from gambling for one minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.40,0:16:19.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,From now on, let's extend the time of the endurance a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:25.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,We were able to cross the first hurdle of the re-start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.86,0:16:29.83,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:42.79,Default 1,,0,0,0,,One more time, together, let's recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.84,0:17:01.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:07.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr...Dr. Fukuhara..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.80,0:17:19.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.74,0:17:24.83,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hello.\NDon't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:27.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,These are people who had the same trouble than Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.10,0:17:31.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:35.77,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:45.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mother, even if these words are tough,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.06,0:17:50.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,it is not an exaggeration to say,\N that the treatment of this disease last a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:51.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,To feel at safe is forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:53.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:56.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,To start again in gambling is a new awake of something,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:58.86,Default 1,,0,0,0,,in the blink of an eye the symptoms will relapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.36,0:18:02.83,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So far, the one that had come to return the debts made by Nami-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:04.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,was you, right?\N{\3c&H533D32&}Yes..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:09.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I have no more savings.\NI see, I'm sure it's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:12.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But from now on, I'd like you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.73,0:18:15.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,to absolutely not help Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:18.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But my daughter is sick, right?\NShouldn't I give her anything she needs..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:22.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,To do that would just worsen Nami-san's condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:25.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You mean if I pay her debts?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:26.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:39.85,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Nami-san will also understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.60,0:18:43.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, her mother too, needs to be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:45.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Prepared?\NIn the worst case..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:48.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,please be prepare to stop living together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:51.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do I have to go that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:53.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I hope that this does not happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:57.78,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, if we think about Nami-san's sake,\Nthat resolution is required.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.46,0:19:00.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:07.70,Default 1,,0,0,0,,To think that somehow the other day\NI went to a pachinko shop
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.30,0:19:10.83,Default 1,,0,0,0,,although I thought it was dangerous,\NI was embezzled by ¥ 40,000
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:14.83,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And that time, I was also thinking\Nabout going to the pachinko shop the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:16.70,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Fukuhara-kun, good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:19.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You were able to proceed with the treatment,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:21.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,at the same time you attended Nami-san's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.46,0:19:22.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.86,0:19:25.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,By the way Fukuhara-kun, did you notice
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:28.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,, that Nami-san is falling in love with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:29.70,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What?\N{\3c&H533D32&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:33.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Fukuhara-kun, \Ncalmly grasp the relationship between doctor and patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:36.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If there were other person but both of them, the treatment wouldn't advance well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:39.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, what about Fukuhara-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:42.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Unconsciously, will you 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.76,0:19:44.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,fall in love with Nami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.43,0:19:50.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That is absolutely impossible!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:54.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.31,0:19:59.35,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.35,0:20:01.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He needn't such a big negative..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.75,0:20:03.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:09.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, Rintaro, listen..\N{\3c&H533D32&}Yumeno-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.76,0:20:11.77,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You came.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:14.27,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting at the examination room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.76,0:20:20.35,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you lend me 10 million,\NI'll be pleased to go to the examination room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:21.85,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino-rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:29.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Rintaro, as expected she's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.26,0:20:32.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Stop your consultation with her already.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:35.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If something happened, you're slow..\N{\3c&H533D32&}Something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:39.77,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about not going beyond the boundaries as a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.77,0:20:41.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It is all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:45.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even if I go beyond,\NI come back at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.03,0:20:47.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even beyond?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.46,0:20:52.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Rintaro, have you fall in love with Yumeno-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:54.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's not about if I love her or hate her,\Nthis is about empathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.06,0:20:56.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What is the difference between empathy and love?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:20:59.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I want to match\Nin attending her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.56,0:21:02.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Isn't that love?!\NYou two, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.16,0:21:05.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's not a conversation to be having in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:06.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.50,0:21:09.77,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about lying you the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.77,0:21:13.27,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I absolutely needed those 10 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.30,0:21:16.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why did you need so much money?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.06,0:21:19.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.83,0:21:23.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Again lend me 10 million, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.06,0:21:26.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.73,0:21:29.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That is the answer to the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,0:21:32.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Tell me why do you need the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.73,0:21:37.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The truth is that you have a man, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.70,0:21:39.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There is no man, it's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:42.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please, En-sama, believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.56,0:21:49.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Okay, however, I have conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.40,0:21:55.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Tonight, you'll have to convince someone at the parlor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:57.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And enliven him with your charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.70,0:22:01.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If that goes well,\NI'll give you 10 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.66,0:22:07.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Come on, just sit here.\N{\3c&H533D32&}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.73,0:22:10.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Though this is the first time I've been called by the senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.43,0:22:12.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It was asked by Dr. Mizushima.\N{\3c&H533D32&}Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.90,0:22:17.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Who is the one that occupies your heart now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.16,0:22:22.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the geisha called Yumeno?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.76,0:22:26.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You mean Yumeno-san..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.30,0:22:29.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,or you mean Akira-san..\N{\3c&H533D32&}Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.73,0:22:31.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I don't know which is the primary personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.30,0:22:34.77,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ta-sama\N{\3c&H533D32&}okay okay what what ...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.66,0:22:37.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Soon, it's my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.76,0:22:40.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mm then a present..\NWhat do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.86,0:22:44.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'd love to receive a ring from Ta-sama.\N{\3c&H533D32&}Then a ring..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.83,0:22:46.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,How much will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:49.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since it's in May, my birthstone is Emerald,\Nso it's expensive
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.36,0:22:52.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,okay..I see..\N{\3c&H533D32&}okay..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.63,0:22:55.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In the treatment of dissociative identity disorder,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.63,0:22:59.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,among the plurality of personalities,\Nwho should be the target of the treatment
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.26,0:23:00.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you would think about it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.70,0:23:02.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because her real name is Akira,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.63,0:23:05.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Akira-san\Nis the original personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.66,0:23:07.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And I'm trying to somehow help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.00,0:23:10.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,However, I think frail Akira-san
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.33,0:23:13.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,would find difficult to overcome the present circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.40,0:23:17.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, Yumeno-san, has been playing an active role\Nas a geisha at Shinbashi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.43,0:23:19.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Although she may cause trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.43,0:23:22.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,she is full of vitality and\Noverflows a mysterious charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.03,0:23:25.33,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That being the case,\Nrather than Akira-san, with the idea of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.36,0:23:27.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,supporting the personality of Yumeno-san
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.56,0:23:28.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,she might have a happy life!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.25,0:23:30.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yup
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.86,0:23:35.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,..that's what I think at the moment, but
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.70,0:23:37.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,senpai, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.50,0:23:39.78,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In my opinion,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.36,0:23:44.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I've reached to an explanation for your mental condition\N at the moment, in one word.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.70,0:23:45.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,One word?\N{\3c&H533D32&}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.50,0:23:49.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's love!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.40,0:23:51.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.26,0:23:54.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder if this fit in countertransference? You..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.23,0:23:57.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's wrong. That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.46,0:23:59.70,Default 1,,0,0,0,,While involving with her,\Nyou've fallen for her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.80,0:24:01.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Well then, conversely, I'll ask you a question.\NSenpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.46,0:24:04.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What do you think it's the difference\Nbetween love and empathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.40,0:24:05.34,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Love and empathy?\N{\3c&H533D32&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.00,0:24:06.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Well Yeah ..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.33,0:24:10.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,well, empathy is until a handshake,\Nto embrace each other, that's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.93,0:24:11.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I agree with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.33,0:24:14.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,When embracing each other, they can't see each other's faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.23,0:24:17.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,how the other party feels\Nis secondary
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.63,0:24:20.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,your own emotions\Ngo first, that's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.66,0:24:24.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Facing face to face,\Nwith reciprocal connection, that's empathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.63,0:24:27.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I want, sincerely,\Nan empathic medical examination with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.86,0:24:30.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Once there is something like love,\NI can't help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.10,0:24:33.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.26,0:24:35.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,About that, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.86,0:24:39.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you're way too serious,\Nand that makes anyone worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.86,0:24:44.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, you know that sometimes the hunter becomes the hunted.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.13,0:24:46.77,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That geisha called Yumeno,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.56,0:24:50.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,seems to be the woman Dir. Ennoji\Nis lavish money on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.10,0:24:50.77,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.26,0:24:54.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,We were waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.76,0:24:56.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.35,0:25:07.35,Default 1,,0,0,0,,My name is Yumeno, I'll serve you one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.26,0:25:19.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.26,0:25:24.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-chan, how nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.25,0:25:28.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ike-chan, you're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.32,0:25:30.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,When looking at your smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.76,0:25:33.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,even the trivial things, by all means, get better
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.75,0:25:37.27,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the pounding that has been a bother\Nis gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.27,0:25:39.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.25,0:25:41.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Okay, drink
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.25,0:25:43.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.74,0:25:46.29,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's good.\N{\3c&H3C2A21&}Yumeno!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.29,0:25:48.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.84,0:25:51.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Oh.. great, great!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.75,0:25:55.27,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.27,0:25:57.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Together we'll mend the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.75,0:25:59.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Let's mend it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.25,0:26:01.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,We'll make money!\N{\3c&H3C2A21&}We'll make money!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.26,0:26:04.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,We'll make money!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.81,0:26:09.85,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.85,0:26:12.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It was for En-sama's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.25,0:26:15.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you're kidding..
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.24,0:26:17.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,wasn't for the 10 million's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.26,0:26:19.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.26,0:26:26.77,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'd like to take you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.77,0:26:29.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.32,0:26:34.27,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So..this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.27,0:26:36.27,Default 1,,0,0,0,,we'll go?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.76,0:26:56.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.28,0:27:00.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.32,0:27:04.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hello? Yumeno-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.76,0:27:08.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,As promised,\NI made a reservation at the restaurant at 12 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.24,0:27:10.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hurry, I'll have you picked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.77,0:27:16.27,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, we'll talk about the money there.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.27,0:27:20.27,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.76,0:27:32.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.\NWhat do you want to drink first?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.25,0:27:34.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah..
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.75,0:27:39.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No, I prefer to make a toast,\NI'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.26,0:27:41.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.74,0:27:56.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.28,0:28:07.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, this is a gift from Mom and Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.56,0:28:11.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Really? Thank you\N{\3c&H3C2A21&}(Ennoji) Prepare your champagne.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.40,0:28:13.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thanks, it's cute.\N{\3c&H3C2A21&}Ah, she's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.20,0:28:17.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Congratulations.\N{\3c&H3C2A21&}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.68,0:28:20.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's great, right?, blow them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.00,0:28:24.27,Remembering,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That child,\Nit would have been better not to have her.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.27,0:28:26.27,Remembering,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't say such a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.27,0:28:30.27,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.75,0:28:38.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh? Yumeno-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.75,0:28:41.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh! Yumeno disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.75,0:28:44.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder if  she didn't like this restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.76,0:28:47.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even though she told me,\Nshe wanted to see the sea in our outing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.24,0:28:50.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I am so sorry.\NI'll locate her at once, and ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.76,0:28:53.82,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's okay, I'm also leaving already.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.82,0:28:57.82,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm really, really\Nsorry for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.25,0:29:13.77,Default 1,,0,0,0,,After I finish with the drying, we'll go for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.77,0:29:17.77,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Coming~
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.26,0:29:23.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah.. hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.76,0:29:27.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno, is she here?\N{\3c&H3C2A21&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.75,0:29:30.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm coming in, for a moment.\N{\3c&H3C2A21&}wait..
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.75,0:29:32.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.75,0:29:34.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.79,0:29:40.35,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.35,0:29:43.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.26,0:29:45.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.26,0:29:54.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Just now, for disturbing you like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.28,0:29:57.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm truly sorry. I apologize\N{\3c&H3C2A21&}No, no. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.26,0:29:59.31,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.31,0:30:02.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse my abrupt question, but
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.25,0:30:07.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,has Yumeno, even to Dr. Hino,\Ndid she innocently ask you money?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.26,0:30:12.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N{\3c&H3C2A21&}Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.26,0:30:15.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr., you're also a victim,\NI'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.76,0:30:20.37,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why is that Yumeno-san\Nwould need so much money?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.37,0:30:23.27,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That child is..
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.27,0:30:26.27,Default 1,,0,0,0,,a pitiful child.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.27,0:30:31.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even though now,\NI'm like a mother for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.25,0:30:34.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the real mother of that child was also a geisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.27,0:30:38.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Despite being a geisha, her mother
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.30,0:30:40.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,gave birth to that child alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.26,0:30:45.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, since the beginning she liked gambling..
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.25,0:30:50.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and she didn't do anything that a mother would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.25,0:30:53.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That child grew up\Nby herself, all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.75,0:30:56.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Having debts everywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.30,0:31:00.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,at the end,\Nshe took money from the geisha house.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.26,0:31:03.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And ran away leaving the girl behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.26,0:31:08.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The previous mother of the Okiya,\Ncouldn't just be indifferent,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.75,0:31:11.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and made her go until high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.24,0:31:14.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,For a while she was steadily\Nworking as an office lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.81,0:31:19.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But her mother appeared again,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.76,0:31:23.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and made that child to pay for her\Ndebts of gambling
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.25,0:31:28.77,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That mother, even now,\Nhas a big influence over Yumeno-san
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.77,0:31:33.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,even to the born of the so called Yumeno personality..
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.26,0:31:34.79,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.79,0:31:38.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumechiyo-san,\Nyou are her mother figure, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.25,0:31:40.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That should be the case, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.75,0:31:43.77,Default 1,,0,0,0,,From now on, our talk is
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.77,0:31:46.77,Default 1,,0,0,0,,becoming an ethics violation,\Nas a psychiatrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.77,0:31:48.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But I want you to know,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.74,0:31:53.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,about Akira-san and the other personality,\NYumeno-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.25,0:32:02.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She suffers from Dissociative identity disorder (DID)
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.77,0:32:06.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why don't you listen to your mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.74,0:32:09.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you bring the 10 million today!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.26,0:32:14.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.25,0:32:22.77,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.77,0:32:25.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.76,0:32:28.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Can she be cured from that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.26,0:32:32.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dissociating, in the form of becoming another personality,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.75,0:32:35.30,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you accustom the mind to avoid\Nrunning away from the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.30,0:32:38.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the circumstances of that extra personality\Ncoming out are few, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.24,0:32:40.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The understanding of the person it's indispensable.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.26,0:32:42.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.26,0:32:44.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.25,0:32:47.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.25,0:32:49.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's from Yumeno-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.25,0:32:50.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.75,0:32:52.77,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.77,0:32:56.34,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I.. don't know why I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.34,0:32:58.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.26,0:33:00.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.76,0:33:03.77,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.77,0:33:06.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I want to disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.25,0:33:11.26,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see. Please, stay there,\NI'll be there soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.26,0:33:14.33,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm going to meet her.\NSo, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.33,0:33:19.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino, about that child's problem,\Nplease take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.75,0:33:21.77,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In this day..
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.77,0:33:24.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,to be alone, and get lost;\Nit's pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.75,0:33:26.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,this day?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.87,0:34:23.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.88,0:34:28.97,Self tought,,0,0,0,,That mound is a symbol of a mother,\Nlooking as the breasts
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.97,0:34:31.37,Self tought,,0,0,0,,that sand mound she is doing now,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.37,0:34:34.88,Self tought,,0,0,0,,it's roundish, smooth and beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.88,0:34:37.88,Self tought,,0,0,0,,Around the mound it's irregular and dirty,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.88,0:34:40.36,Self tought,,0,0,0,,this division alone is intense,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.36,0:34:44.87,Self tought,,0,0,0,,Maybe she has suffered some kind of abuse from her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.87,0:34:47.92,Self tought,,0,0,0,,Even now she is seeking for a mother, but
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.92,0:34:51.89,Self tought,,0,0,0,,ultimately she has repeatedly been betrayed\Nand disillusioned..
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.89,0:34:56.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mom, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.87,0:35:07.37,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr..
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.37,0:35:22.37,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.38,0:35:30.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr.\NWhy did you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.88,0:35:36.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You sound like being troubled,\Nsomehow, I wanted to lend you some strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.37,0:35:43.37,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Has something similar to this time, happened at times, before?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.38,0:35:52.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's okay not to answer,\Nif you don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.40,0:36:02.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.86,0:36:25.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr., why did you become a mind's doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.89,0:36:27.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.39,0:36:34.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because..
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.39,0:36:45.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,My mother committed suicide when I was in junior high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.96,0:36:52.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,My mother had been suffering from depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.38,0:36:57.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, I\Ndidn't pay attention to her mind's illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.89,0:37:00.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,to my continuously depressed mother
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.89,0:37:04.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I kept saying "try your best".
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.41,0:37:12.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I've cornered my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.38,0:37:13.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even that morning..
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.38,0:37:26.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.95,0:37:32.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't have tea.\NI'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.89,0:37:36.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rintaro
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.39,0:37:41.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mom too, try your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.95,0:37:52.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.38,0:38:03.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That day,\Nmy mother jumped in front of the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.87,0:38:08.87,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If at that time
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.87,0:38:13.98,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I had drunk the tea that my mother offered me..
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.98,0:38:16.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If at that time
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.88,0:38:23.37,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I had properly listened\Nto what my mother wanted to tell me..
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.37,0:38:26.37,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even now I think of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.86,0:38:31.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, the "If"s of the past
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.91,0:38:35.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,no matter how much I consider them,\NI can't regain them.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.46,0:39:01.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.87,0:39:17.37,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If I'd had a talent for making people laugh,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.37,0:39:20.87,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I would have liked to become a comedian.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.43,0:39:25.47,Default 1,,0,0,0,,When my mother died,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.47,0:39:29.37,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I became unable to feel anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.37,0:39:32.37,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the tears didn't come out anymore..
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.37,0:39:35.87,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I didn't even know whether I was sad or what.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.38,0:39:40.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I thought I was done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.40,0:39:44.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be laughing or crying anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.95,0:39:50.37,Default 1,,0,0,0,,that was what I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.37,0:39:54.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, after about half a year, there was a day,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.88,0:39:57.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,when on the TV, I heard a story\Nalmost ridiculous
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.88,0:40:00.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and when I realized I was laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.88,0:40:05.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,At that moment,\Nfrom inside of my chest, for a long time, from inside
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.92,0:40:10.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,feelings that couldn't be explain with words\Nsuddenly overflowed..
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.88,0:40:17.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I thought it was an amazing thing to laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.38,0:40:22.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since then I've been supporting heartily that comedian.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.88,0:40:27.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But unfortunately to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.91,0:40:30.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I had no talent for making people laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.96,0:40:36.37,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, I went with my second choice,\Nand I became a psychiatrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.37,0:40:38.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,After talking about such a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.39,0:40:42.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I lose completely the reliance as a psychiatrist
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.88,0:40:49.87,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.87,0:40:52.87,Default 1,,0,0,0,,for telling me your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.97,0:40:58.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I should be the one saying thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.39,0:41:03.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,At last,\Nwe could drink tea together in this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.88,0:41:19.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.88,0:41:23.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, you were also alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.39,0:41:32.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira-san,\Nyou're not the only one who feels lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.45,0:41:39.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,At that time, when he made me laugh,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.88,0:41:42.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,my favorite comedian, said this,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.89,0:41:45.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Everyone is basically lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.89,0:41:49.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because they're lonely,\Nthey do such things as work desperately,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.88,0:41:52.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}they make friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.36,0:41:56.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}they fall in love,\Nin order not to be lonely."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.45,0:42:13.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.88,0:42:15.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.44,0:42:23.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,would..
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.38,0:42:30.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Would you stay close, from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.87,0:42:35.87,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.87,0:42:40.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll be by your side from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.36,0:43:22.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.12,0:43:40.87,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry, even on a holiday.\N{\3c&H3C2A21&}It's okay, even at home,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.87,0:43:44.37,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'd only feel irritated\N{\3c&H3C2A21&}irritated..
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.88,0:43:48.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Psychiatrists are troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.88,0:43:50.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.38,0:43:53.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,About that, I think it's a good thing to be a surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.44,0:43:57.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,When there's something bad,\Nyou just take it off at once, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.36,0:44:02.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I might also have a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.38,0:44:06.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is it okay?\NIt's not herbal tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.87,0:44:12.37,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Cheers for god work.\N{\3c&H3C2A21&}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.94,0:44:22.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Prof., have you ever fallen in love with patients?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.38,0:44:23.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.89,0:44:29.37,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That wasn't a mistake, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.37,0:44:31.87,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Could it be?\Nthat you fall in love with me
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.87,0:44:33.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No..sorry..
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.88,0:44:36.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I got drunk with one cup..
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.87,0:44:48.37,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry for being late,\NI returned with Yumeno-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.88,0:44:56.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.90,0:45:00.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.39,0:45:09.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno, congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.38,0:45:12.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sis Yumeno,\NHappy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.88,0:45:14.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.88,0:45:18.37,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Every year, since you dislike it,\Nwe can't celebrate it,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.37,0:45:21.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But as it's such an important day, from now on,\Nwe will properly celebrate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.91,0:45:23.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, sit down, sit down
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.94,0:45:26.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Happy birthday to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.90,0:45:30.37,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Happy birthday to you..
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.37,0:45:32.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Happy birthday..
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.88,0:45:36.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno, Yumeno!\N{\3c&H3C2A21&}Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.39,0:45:43.98,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.98,0:45:46.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira-san
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.88,0:45:50.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.39,0:45:57.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.38,0:46:01.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm handing over,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.40,0:46:04.97,Default 1,,0,0,0,,what you left behind the other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.97,0:46:12.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.39,0:46:16.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I..
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.38,0:46:19.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it was a good thing to be born..
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.88,0:46:23.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.39,0:46:26.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira-san
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.39,0:46:29.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure it's good.\Nisn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.96,0:46:51.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.38,0:47:21.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.48,0:47:25.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.36,0:47:47.87,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What kind of dog was\NYasuke's mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.87,0:47:50.87,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.87,0:47:53.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.88,0:47:55.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.88,0:48:03.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm Yumeno's mother,\Nand I have something to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.42,0:48:06.87,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You..what did you do to Yumeno?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.87,0:48:10.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That girl suddenly started to act strange.\NIsn't it your fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.89,0:48:14.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You were together today also, right?\NWhat did you do to Yumeno!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.88,0:48:21.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr...\NI wonder if you could help..
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.39,0:48:24.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,10 million is fine\Nto save that girl from trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.96,0:48:26.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mother.\N{\3c&H3C2A21&}eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.88,0:48:30.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Today, do you what day is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.40,0:48:32.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What day?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.36,0:48:36.87,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Today, it's Akira-san's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.87,0:48:38.87,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.87,0:48:42.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's just that I don't celebrate\Nsuch dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.42,0:48:47.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mother, you might have it hard too,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.36,0:48:52.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,but, you go further and want to cause pain to Akira-san
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.38,0:48:56.37,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No matter how many cruel things\Nyou did to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.37,0:49:01.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No matter how many awful things you said to her,\NAkira-san
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.38,0:49:05.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,is willing to forgive you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.96,0:49:10.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,she wants to be loved by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.39,0:49:14.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for Akira-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.88,0:49:23.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You, in some way,\Nresemble Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.90,0:49:27.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I mean the smell..
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.95,0:49:30.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Could it be that you too,\Nstill miss the breasts
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.39,0:49:32.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,of your mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.88,0:49:40.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,to begin with, why don't you have the scent of a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.88,0:49:44.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Although you have money and prestige
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.40,0:49:48.87,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Have you already sleep with Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.87,0:49:52.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,so uncool
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.38,0:49:57.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Your mother was a woman like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.40,0:49:59.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,sluttish with men
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.89,0:50:04.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H3C2A21&}because of that, you became sort of scared of\Ngoing out with women?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.40,0:50:09.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Lucky guess!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.39,0:50:14.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Really!\NYou and my Akira are really alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.38,0:50:20.37,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.37,0:50:23.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This mom with such an elegant face
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.41,0:50:25.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,had an affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.48,0:50:31.98,Default 1,,0,0,0,,With someone like you as a mother,\Nit would have been better not to have one.
